text: Kashkakovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Shulganovsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 481 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 47 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 7 km from Shulganovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Kashkakovo
